Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US-China relations warm
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wclq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Jun 1981
US-China arms deal announced as first plans to start disarmament talks with Soviets are unveiled. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less